<Author>GKA33
<Content>Nightmare weekend When I first arrive to the hotel I went directly to the reception and she charge my credit card for the total amount of the stay (4 nights) without showing my room. When I went to my room, it was completely full of mosquitoes. I went back to the recepcionist and she was looking for spray to kill them forgetting that it was a room with air conditioning and no ventilation. I request another room. At the beginning, she told me that there was no room available like the one I had. I agree to move to smaller room and when I turn the air conditioning on, there were more mosquitoes in this room, the bed sheets smelled horrible, the bath tub had a big leak and the curtains were full of dirt. Then, I decide to cancel the reservation and go back to my home although the trip was two and half hours. When I went to the receptionist to make the arrangements for my money, they told me that the policy of the hotel was that if you do a cancellation they will not return the money back independently of the situation. So, they didn't gave me my money and I can't stay at the facilities. My children were very sad and my husband and I were upset because they take the money and didn't giving us the service we deserve. 
