<Content>Never stay here! Never consider this hotel if you want to have a good time or at least a friendly, respectable staff. I considered this hotel because of the information in the Frommers travel guide. I made a reservation for two days by phone and asked about the water and swimming conditions. They told me there was clean, clear water and that there were few waves and good snorkneling conditions. When we came there it was exactly the opposite. The water was not clean but dirty and muddy, there were lots of waves and stones sticking out of the water and near hotel there was a lot of garbage. We told them it's not what they told us about the hotel and it wasn't acceptable and we can't stay here. We asked to speak to manager, but he refused to meet us. As a result we idn't stay at this hotel and they charged our credit card 112$ because of their cancellation policy. Do not stay at this hotel!!! 
